  "title": "Veterinary Assistant #81436",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Animal Clinic</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Veterinary Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Yio Chu Kang</li><li>Working Hours: 4 days/week (Mon-Sat: 9.30am-1pm, 3pm-7.30pm), closed Sundays/public holidays</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic $2,000 - $3,500</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the reception desk and help with client questions.</li><li>Assist vets with daily tasks and during consultations.</li><li>Check anaesthesia levels and help in surgery.</li><li>Support hospital treatments and run lab tests.</li><li>Assist with diagnostic imaging.</li><li>Complete administrative duties when needed.</li><li>Help manage clinic stock.</li><li>Keep the clinic clean and hygienic.</li><li>Care for animals and help clean up after sick or recovering pets.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Preferably has a Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in Sciences (Biology, Chemistry, Biotechnology, Veterinary Bioscience, or similar).</li><li>At least 1 year of experience working with animals is preferred.</li><li>Suitable for those who are caring, dependable, and comfortable working with animals.</li><li>Career path includes chances to take on supervisory roles.</li><li>Must be able to work weekends on a rotating 4-day work week.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81436 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
